gov.usgs.anss.edgeoutput

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.edgeoutput.Module

  • public final class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used statically on each received TraceBuf, to allow assembly of frags, checking of sequences for each institution, module, and port of receipt. In July 2010, it started doing the frags as the frag code was moved out of the TraceBufListener when more frags had n packets.
